Trinity::

She looked up at Aerotaur and sniffled.  She took a few steps closer 
to him and put her paw on his foot. She wasn't sure what to do. She 
knew her parents were now gone for good and not coming back. She 
looked up at him, then looked down. "I'll try not to be any trouble 
to you sir.  I promise to be good.  I'll even get those maximals for 
you. I'll be good."  she started crying again.  She whispered 
again,"Sorry mom."
